INSTALLATION------------*nix:----->python setup.py install  Windows:--------If you have mingw installed, type:>python setup.py build --compiler=mingw32 install(Note: It is recommended to use VC Express compiler for Python versions >2.6. Thereare some DLL problems regarding MingW compiled extensions on Python >2.6 versions.)Tested Python versions:-----------------------v0.62 works from Python2.4 till Python3.2. Yes, a single rep.Tested Platforms:-----------------v0.62 tested on Solaris 10, Ubuntu 10-11(32-64bit), MacOSX Snow Leopard 10.6,FreeBSD 8.1 and some other Linux distros, too.